Scavenger/Injector/Manterror/Bumblebee/Scattershot:



Scavenger swerved, acid hitting the left side of his vehicle mode, eating at 
his armor plating.  Raising both machien guns on his sides, and the laser 
cannon mounted on the top of his HUMVEE mode, he fired off twenty 
armor-piercing round and a single laser blast at Mosquitor, continuing after 
Dinobot.

---

Injector dive bombed, charging upwards at Prowl, firing two stinger missiles 
at the middle of his pelvis.

---

Bumblebee fired two optic blasts at Iron Raptor, the robot in Prowl's 
feathered arms.  (They are feathered...right?)

---

Scattershot chuckled.  "Mercy.  UGH!  Everybody, let's rock!  Walk this way!" 
he raised his rifle, firing off 5 shells at Prowl's back.
